@JohnSmith-b6n yeah that is fair enough. I can't remember where I found the calculators but it might be worth finding one or running the numbers.

I remember watching one that looked at Germany where prices had increased enormously after Russia's invasion of Ukraine. In that analysis they showed that even much more efficient card would take years to save $100 even if it was under a gaming load like 8-12 hours a day.

I don't have any agenda here nor know enough to say anything about your situation, I am just suggesting it might be worth a look. If there is a major price difference for more efficiency, you might take a long time to break even on that.
